data.description: Enjoy the serenity of this quaint neighborhood just minutes away from downtown. This brick mid-century abounds with character and boasts a large formal living room with gas fireplace, dining room, and an open den/kitchen. The kitchen has quartz counters, stainless appliances, and a walk-in pantry. Down the hall you will find TONS of storage, 2 spacious guest rooms, renovated hall bath, and a lovely master suite with a walk-in tiled shower. There's more... all new light fixtures, windows, interior and exterior doors! On the home's exterior you will find beautiful landscaping serviced by an all yard sprinkler system and drip for the flower beds, a 10x10 lawn mower shed, and a workshop with electricity. The back porch is an oasis and leads to a paver patio with gazebo and firepit and part of the yard is fenced. A one car carport with 3 storage closets, an RV pad with 50 amp electric hookup, geothermal water heater, Culligan water softener and purifier are bonuses. Call Sara to view!
